@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About me</PageTitle>
<div class="">
    <div class="about-card">
        <header class="about-hero">
            <div class="avatar-ring">
                <div class="avatar-placeholder">
                    <img src="img/gab.jpg" width="180" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <h1>Gabriel Burrola</h1>
            <h4>Migra</h4>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">.NET Full Stack Developer  •  Trance | EDM Music Producer & DJ </p>
        </header>

        <section class="about-section accent-panel">
            <div class="section-title-row">
                <span class="section-kicker">01</span>
                <h2>About Me</h2>
            </div>
            <p>
                Hi, my name is Gabriel Burrola, and I’m a passionate .NET Full Stack Developer focused on building elegant,
                modern, and scalable digital experiences. I enjoy transforming ideas into polished applications that combine
                strong backend architecture, intuitive UI design, and reliable performance.
            </p>
            <p>
                My work centers around the Microsoft ecosystem, where I love crafting solutions with C#, ASP.NET Core, Blazor, MVC, 
                REST APIs, SQL, and cloud services. I’m driven by clean code, thoughtful UX, and the challenge of turning complex
                business needs into software that feels simple, fast, and useful.
            </p>
            <p>
                I've been passionate about Trance & EDM music since late 90s, so I started getting involved into music production and DJing 
                ever since, you can find some cool stuff on my YouTube channel (link at the bottom of this page).
            </p>
            <p>
                I've also had the opportunity to learn and work in graphic design and audio and video post-production.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section glass-panel">
            <div class="section-title-row">
                <span class="section-kicker">02</span>
                <h2>About DiagramER</h2>
            </div>
            <div style="width:100% !important; text-align:center !important;">
                <img src="img/diagramerlogo.png" width="150" />
            </div>
            <p>
                <a href="/" class="diagramer-link">DiagramER</a> is an interactive database diagramming tool built with Blazor and .NET, designed to make schema design feel
                visual, flexible, and modern. It allows users to create tables, define columns, configure metadata such as datatype,
                length, default value, nullability, and primary keys, and then connect related fields through drag-and-drop relations.
            </p>
            <p>
                The application also includes smart relation routing, editable relation names, draggable labels, JSON import/export,
                diagram export, zoom and pan controls, and a responsive canvas experience inspired by traditional database design tools.
                The goal of DiagramER is to provide a clean and intuitive way to model database structures directly in the browser.
            </p>
        </section>

